<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3074] SimpleTextCodec needs SimpleText DocValues impl</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3074</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;currently SimpleTextCodec uses binary docValues we should move that to a simple text impl.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
